  <brief_title>Efficacy of Gelatin Tannate in Treatment Acute Gastroenteritis in Children.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Gelatin Tannate in Treatment Acute Gastroenteritis in Children: A Double Blind Randomized, Placebo- Controlled Trial .</official_title>
