  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  children &lt; 5 years old

          -  diarrhea (defined as the passage of 3 or more loose or watery stools per day) for &gt; 1
             day but &lt; 5 days

          -  inform consent sign

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  regularly used antibiotics, probiotics, gelatin tannate, diosmectite, racecadotril
             within 7 days before admission

          -  underlying gastrointestinal tract disorder presenting with diarrhea

          -  breastfeeding &gt;50%

          -  malnutrition (weight/high &lt;3pc)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
